9qns3bgb,ilve-umi09qns3bgc,ilve-umi09qns3bgg,ilve-umi09qns3bgp,ilve-umi09qns3bkb,ilve-umi09qns3bkc,ilve-umi09qns3bkg,ilve-umi09qns3bkp,ilve-umi09qns3bub,ilve-umi09qns3buc,ilve-umi09qns3bug,ilve-umi09qns3bup,ilve-umi09qns3egb,ilve-umi09qns3egc,ilve-umi09qns3egg,ilve-umi09qns3egp,ilve-umi09qns3mbb,ilve-umi09qns3mbc,ilve-umi09qns3mbg,ilve-umi09qns3mbp,ilve-umi09qns3mgb,ilve-umi09qns3mgc,ilve-umi09qns3mgg,ilve-umi09qns3mgp,ilve-umi09qns3rab,ilve-umi09qns3rac,ilve-umi09qns3rag,ilve-umi09qns3rap,ilve-umi09qns3ssb,ilve-umi09qns3ssc,ilve-umi09qns3ssg,ilve-umi09qns3ssp,ilve-umi09qns3whb,ilve-umi09qns3whc,ilve-umi09qns3whg,ilve-umi09qns3whp\", \"Variant Count\": 80, \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>With a total oven capacity of 3.5 cu. ft., a 4.3-inch full-touch oven control display, an easy-clean enamel oven cavity, and a combination of traditional Italian design and modern technology, the Majestic 36-inch induction range is unmatched.</p><p>Currently Available: Yes</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>The show-stopping range cooker that will turn your kitchen into a showpiece.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that exudes elegance and functionality in equal measure. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies. Despite its ability to blend into any setting, Majestic commands attention.</p><p></p><p>The sculpted, meticulously detailed forms of majestic range cookers, crafted from pure steel, make them eye-catching kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative accents.</p><p></p><p>Designed for your home's kitchen, these workhorses are available in a variety of colors (from 30 to 60 inches) and set-up options (from multiple options) and can be customized to RAL Classic shades upon request. They also feature fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Indictor for residual heat</li><li>Timer with built-in self-exclusion</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Function that boosts</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Ensuring children's safety</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Prevention of overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Drawer and door with a gentle closing mechanism</li><li>Getting started with little</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Product Technology</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, guaranteeing the best satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Range</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Induction Range (Oven)</strong></p><p>Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) are a modern, practical, and safe method of cooking that combines cutting-edge technology with an elegant and modern aesthetic. Induction offers many benefits, such as safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measurement of Persistent Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Timer with Built-in Stop Function</strong></p><p>Once the specified time has passed, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Bridge Management</strong></p><p>If your induction cooktop (hob) has this capability, you can treat two adjacent zones as one and use a single command to control them both.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Protecting Children</strong></p><p>After you enable this feature, you can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><p><strong>Keeping Things From Overheating and Leaking Liquids</strong></p><p>An automatic shutoff mechanism activates in the event of a liquid spill or overheating of the cooktop (hob).</p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Oven Solutions</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Impressive Size and Power: The Ovens.</strong></p><p>No matter if you go with a single or double combination oven, our 36-inch range offers enough room for even the largest of dishes\\u2014its capacity is up to 4 cubic feet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>The oven's temperature stays consistent throughout thanks to the electronic control, unlike with traditional ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></p><p>The display's use of TFT technology guarantees excellent readability by displaying concise and clear graphics for each function.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>With a single touch of the big screen, you can control all the features of either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously. You can set the temperature, set the timer, and program the ovens to start and stop cooking automatically.</p><p></p><p><strong>Silent Closing Door System</strong></p><p>With the shock absorber installed in the door hinges, closing the door is a more gradual and noiseless process.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cabinet with Warming Drawer and Soft-Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Probe for Cooking</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection (Cooking in Wet Conditions)</strong></p><p>You can achieve a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast thanks to this system, which removes the vapors from inside the cavity, allowing you to choose a drier or more moist cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Inspiring Cooling Air and Dense Insulation</strong></p><p>Keeps the kitchen and its furniture from getting too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grill Coil that Folds for Easy Cleaning</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Dishwasher Safe Enamel</strong></p><p>Grease is easier to remove since it does not adhere to the surface.</p><p></p><p><strong>Baking Processes. UOV 80 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li>The pizza party</li><li>Warming up</li><li>Very intense cooking</li><li>Getting started with little</li><li>Extremely moist cooking</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Suspended cooking</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Preparing moist food from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Standard static cooking with moisture</li><li>Using a number of fans to cook</li><li>Several wet fan ovens</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Party Pizza</strong></p><p>This oven is perfect for baking pizza, bread, focaccia, and other similar foods. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and it works in tandem with the other, less powerful heating elements to provide the ideal conditions for baking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Warming up</strong></p><p>Guarantees rapid thawing of any and all frozen foods, bringing them to room temperature without changing their flavor or texture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking to the Extremes</strong></p><p>This steam-discharge cooker guarantees rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for foods that require a crunchy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, fish with a salt crust, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Easy Beginning</strong></p><p>With the fast preheating function, you can quickly get to the temperature you want, and then select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. What's more, when set to a low temperature, it can also function as rapid defrosting.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>For moist cooking, such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, chicken cacciatore, etc., it ensures rapid and intense cooking with steam block.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling with a Fan</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking on a Grill with a Closed Door</strong></p><p>Functions such as quick and deep grilling, browning, roasting, and cooking fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and vegetables are highly recommended.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc., all benefit from browning and the finishing touch of color that this function provides.</p><p></p><p><strong>Delicately Cooked Food from Above</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Lessons in Home Cooking</strong></p><p>Pastries (such as biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, and so on) are best cooked in this way to finish the cooking cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>In-Depth Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Cooking with Moist Static</strong></p><p>This makes traditional static cooking even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>You can bake a variety of foods at once without worrying about their aromas blending\\u2014lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc.\\u2014and save both time and energy thanks to this feature.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>When cooking with multiple fans, this increases the moisture content.</p><p></p><p><strong>Sustainable Food Preparation</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Question 65 in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Danger to Health and Fertility</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">www<span>Warnings.ca.gov (P65)</span></a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/wKi6ZYNcCxY.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/re1Uo4qdmcc.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/4JuPNm3uQqU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> </div></div><br/><br/><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br/><br/></div></div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_features\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" data-slug=\\\"features\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_features\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Features</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_features\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_features\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"> <div><div><div><li><strong>Simple to Clean Enamel Cooktop Inside</strong></li></div><div>Grease is easier to remove since it does not adhere to the surface.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Easy Clean Enamel Oven Interior\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1380.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Burner Made of Nanotechnology and Finished in a Satin Black Finish</strong></li></div><div>An elegant Total Black finish complements the noble technical characteristics of brass, which are enhanced with a nanotechnological coating that guarantees easy cleaning.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Total Black Brass Burner With Non-Stick Nanotechnological Coating\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1447.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Gas Range with Cast-Iron Pan Holders</strong></li></div><div>You can rest assured that your pots will be well-supported by the sturdy cast-iron pan supports.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Cooktop (Hob) With Cast Iron Pan Supports\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1448.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Expertly Crafted Stovetops</strong></li></div><div>Crafted from AISI 304 steel with a 12/10 thickness, this versatile cooktop is available in a variety of configurations and can be used with gas or induction burners.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Highly Specialized Cooktops\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1449.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Standard Features: Two Gas Burners Capable of Producing Up to 20,000 BTU</strong></li></div><div>For every kind of cooking, the ideal supply and distribution of heat.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Dual Gas Burners With Power Up To 20000 BTU As Standard\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1474.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>A Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></li></div><div>The TFT technology ensures a very readable display, showing all functions with clear and immediate graphics. With a single touch of the big screen, you can control both the single oven and the two ovens simultaneously. With one touch, you can set the temperature, set the timer, and program the automatic start and end of cooking.</div><div><img alt=\\\"4.3 Inch Full Touch Display\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1475.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>The Eminent Proclamation of Ilve</strong></li></div><div>Majestic is a daring and expert representation of the ideal range cooker; its rounded forms, forged in pure steel with painstakingly made details, will adorn your home with their beauty and functionality, which is a marriage of traditional Italian style and modern technology.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Ilve\\u2019S Majestic Statement\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1496.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>The Show-Stopping Range Cooker That Will Transform Your Kitchen</strong></li></div><div>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that guarantee the best satisfaction by combining top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness.</div><div><img alt=\\\"The Statement Range Cooker Which Makes Your Kitchen Unique\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1497.jpg\\\"/></div></div> </div> </div></div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_specification\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" data-slug=\\\"specification\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_specification\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Specifications</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_specification\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_specification\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"> <ul><li><strong>Brand</strong>: ILVE</li><li><strong>Series</strong>: Majestic II</li><li><strong>Appliance Category</strong>: Range</li><br/><p><strong>Appearance</strong></p><li><strong>Color</strong>: Antique White</li><li><strong>Color Family</strong>: Antique White</li><li><strong>Design Style</strong>: Retro Style</li><li><strong>Trim</strong>: Burnished</li><br/><p><strong>Dimensions</strong></p><li><strong>Exterior Width</strong>: 36\\u2033</li><li><strong>Width</strong>: 35 7/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Depth</strong>: 29\\u2033</li><li><strong>Height</strong>: 38 3/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Depth with Door Opened at 90 Degrees</strong>: 42 7/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Product Weight (lbs)</strong>: 248</li><br/><p><strong>Fuel Type</strong></p><li><strong>Fuel Type</strong>: Electric</li><br/><p><strong>Style</strong></p><li><strong>Style</strong>: Freestanding</li><li><strong>Control Location</strong>: Front</li><br><p><strong>Capacity</strong></p><li><strong>Total Capacity (cu. ft.)</strong>: 3.5</li><li><strong>Number of Ovens</strong>: Single Oven</li><li><strong>Main Oven Capacity (cu. ft.)</strong>: 3.5</li><br><p><strong>Cooking Surface</strong></p><li><strong>Cooktop Configuration</strong>: Induction</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Type</strong>: Induction Element</li><li><strong>Number of Burners/Elements</strong>: 5</li><li><strong>Grill</strong>: No</li><li><strong>Griddle</strong>: No</li><li><strong>French Top</strong>: No</li><li><strong>Highest Element Output</strong>: 3700 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N1</strong>: 3200 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N2</strong>: 3700 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N3</strong>: 2500 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N4</strong>: 2500 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N5</strong>: 1800 Watts</li><br><p><strong>Oven</strong></p><li><strong>Oven Control Type</strong>: TFT Electronic Touchscreen</li><li><strong>Oven Door Type</strong>: Triple Glass Door</li><li><strong>Oven Cleaning Type</strong>: Easy Clean Enamel Cavities</li><li><strong>Main Oven Type</strong>: UOV 80 E3 TFT S</li><li><strong>Interior Width</strong>: 26 3/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Interior Height</strong>: 14 3/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Interior Depth</strong>: 16 1/8\\u2033</li><br><p><strong>Technical Details</strong></p><li><strong>Voltage</strong>: 240</li><li><strong>Amps</strong>: 66</li><br/><p><strong>Certifications</strong></p><li><strong>Star-K Certified</strong>: Yes</li><br/><p><str