tps://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_170061.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_170062.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_170063.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_147927-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_147928-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_33226.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_33225.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_147929-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_147930-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_147931-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_147932-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3BGG_p13582_33197.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"8690.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202237246\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>With a total oven capacity of 3.5 cu. ft., a 4.3-inch full-touch oven control display, an easy-clean enamel oven cavity, and a combination of traditional Italian design and modern technology, the Majestic 36-inch induction range is unmatched.</p><p>Product Status: Available</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that effortlessly integrates into any space while commanding attention with its striking combination of form and function. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies that are both practical and aesthetically pleasing.</p><p></p><p>The graceful curves and meticulously crafted details of majestic range cookers make them beautiful additions to any home.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Signal for remaining heat</li><li>Scheduler with built-in timeout</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Function that boosts</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Ensuring the safety of children</li><li>Screen size: 4.3 inches Full Touch</li><li>Safety from overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Cabinet and door soft-closing mechanism</li><li>A brief overview</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Technology for Products</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that guarantee the best satisfaction by combining top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Range</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Induction Range (Oven)</strong></p><p>With their modern technology and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) make cooking a breeze. Induction facilitates the preparation of dishes and recipes with its many benefits, including safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed.</p><p></p><p><strong>Determinant of Remaining Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>Once the specified time has passed, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>With this function, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Capability</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>The induction cooktop (hob) cannot be turned on using the controls once this feature has been enabled and will remain so until disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Prevention of Overheating and Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>A safety feature will activate and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Ovens: Massive Capacity and Peak Efficiency.</strong></p><p>Our 36-inch range has a capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven that will give you plenty of room, even for large dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Electronic Temperature Control with High Precision</strong></p><p>Unlike with traditional ovens, the temperature of the oven will stay consistent thanks to the electronic control.</p><p></p><p><strong>A 4.3-inch Full-Touch Screen</strong></p><p>The display guarantees excellent readability with TFT technology, showing every function with clear and immediate graphics.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>Control all the functions of the single oven or both ovens with a single device: temperature, timer, and automatic cooking start and end programmer\\u2014all with one touch and at a glance\\u2014on the large display.</p><p></p><p><strong>Door with a System for Soft Closing</strong></p><p>A shock absorber is integrated into the door hinges, allowing for a quieter and more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Soft-Closing Mechanism for the Warming Drawer</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Probe for Cooking</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Evaporation for Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>You can achieve a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast thanks to this system, which removes the vapors from inside the cavity, allowing you to choose a drier or more moist cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Celsius range of 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Inspiring Cooling Air and Dense Insulation</strong></p><p>Ensures that the kitchen and its adjacent furniture do not become too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>The Ultimate Cleaning Solution: A Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rinse-Free Enamel</strong></p><p>The grease slides off the surface and is easier to wipe off.</p><p></p><p><strong>Features of the Oven. UOV 80 E3 TFT Silver</strong></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li>The pizza party</li><li>Removing From Freeze</li><li>Cooking to extremes</li><li>Fast start</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Steaming food cooked in the air</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Preparing moist food from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Damp static regular cooking</li><li>Numerous fan-assisted cooking methods</li><li>Various wet fan cooking methods</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Party Pizza</strong></p><p>Perfect for baking pizza, bread, and focaccia. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and with the assistance of the other, less powerful heating elements, it produces the ideal conditions for this kind of cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing From Freeze</strong></p><p>Guarantees rapid thawing of any and all frozen foods, bringing them to room temperature without changing their flavor or texture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>Its steam discharge ensures rapid and intense cooking, making it ideal for foods that require a crunchy texture, such as baked potatoes and vegetables, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Easy Beginning</strong></p><p>With the fast preheating function, you can quickly get to the temperature you want, and then select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. What's more, when set to a low temperature, it can also function as rapid defrosting.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extremely Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Searing on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>Many foods, including sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc., can be cooked quickly and thoroughly with this function, which also significantly reduces energy consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling in a Room with No Doors Open</strong></p><p>Functions such as quick and deep grilling, browning, roasting, and cooking fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and vegetables are highly recommended.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc., all benefit from browning and the finishing touch of color that this function provides.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes from Above</strong></p><p>Perfect for browning and finishing the color of a wide variety of foods without mushiness.</p><p></p><p><strong>Back to the Basics: Cooking</strong></p><p>With the exception of leavened desserts (biscuits, meringues, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking pastries.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes Made from Scratch</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Cooking with Moist Static</strong></p><p>This makes traditional static cooking even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>You can bake a variety of foods at once without worrying about their aromas blending\\u2014lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc.\\u2014and save both time and energy thanks to this feature.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>When cooking with multiple fans, this increases the moisture content.</p><p></p><p><strong>Sustainable Food Preparation</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measure 65 in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Danger to Health and Fertility</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">www<span>Visit P65Warnings.