/div><span><bdi><span>$</span>242.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"RAL\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Burnished\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 36 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 5 Elements, 3.5 cu. ft. Total Oven Capacity (RAL / Chrome / Triple Glass Door) - UMI09NS3RAC\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMI09NS3RAC\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3RAC_p13650.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3RAC_p13650.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3RAC_p13650_170190.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3RAC_p13650_170191.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3RAC_p13650_170192.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3RAC_p13650_33780.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3RAC_p13650_33781.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3RAC_p13650_33782.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09NS3RAC_p13650_11044.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"11490.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202255639\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>Combining traditional Italian design with modern technology, the Majestic 36-inch induction range boasts a total oven capacity of 3.5 cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean, and 5 precise and efficient element zones.</p><p>Availability: 90 - 120 days for pre-order</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>The show-stopping range cooker that will turn your kitchen into a showpiece.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that exudes elegance and functionality in equal measure. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies. Despite its ability to blend into any setting, Majestic commands attention.</p><p></p><p>The sculpted, meticulously detailed forms of majestic range cookers, crafted from pure steel, make them eye-catching kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative accents.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Measurement of remaining heat</li><li>Scheduler with built-in timeout</li><li>Bridge management</li><li>Enhancement feature</li><li>Handles for sliding</li><li>Ensuring the safety of children</li><li>Widescreen 4.3-inch</li><li>Safeguarding against overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Drawer and door with a gentle closing mechanism</li><li>Fast start</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Innovations in Product Technologies</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that guarantee the best satisfaction by combining top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies related to stovetops</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Induction Range (Oven)</strong></p><p>Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) are a modern, practical, and safe method of cooking that combines cutting-edge technology with an elegant and modern aesthetic. Induction offers many benefits, such as safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measurement of Persistent Heat</strong></p><p>The glass is hot, so be careful not to touch it or put anything on it; doing so could cause damage.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>Activates the active zone until the timer goes off.</p><p></p><p><strong>Managing Bridges</strong></p><p>With this function, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Puts the induction cooktop's (hob's) full power into the predetermined area, allowing you to boil and cook more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>By simply gliding your finger from side to side, you can adjust the operating temperature, for instance, thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>The induction cooktop (hob) cannot be turned on using the controls once this feature has been enabled and will remain so until disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Protecting Against Overheating and Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>An automatic shutoff mechanism activates in the event of a liquid spill or overheating of the cooktop (hob).</p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Impressive Size and Power: The Ovens.</strong></p><p>Our 36-inch range has a capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven that will give you plenty of room, even for large dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Controlling Temperature with Electronic Precision</strong></p><p>The oven's temperature stays consistent throughout thanks to the electronic control, unlike with traditional ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></p><p>The screen guarantees excellent legibility with TFT technology, showing every function with clear and immediate graphics.</p><p></p><p><strong>The TFT display is user-friendly, comprehensive, and has a high resolution.</strong></p><p>Control all the functions of the single oven or both ovens with a single device: temperature, timer, and automatic cooking start and end programmer\\u2014all with one touch and at a glance\\u2014on the large display.</p><p></p><p><strong>Silent Closing Door System</strong></p><p>With the shock absorber installed in the door hinges, closing the door is a more gradual and noiseless process.</p><p></p><p><strong>Soft-Closing Mechanism for the Warming Drawer</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Food Preparation Assessment Tool</strong></p><p>The tool you need to check the internal temperature of meat, among other things.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection for Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>With this system, the vapours are drawn out from within the cavity, giving you the option for a more or less moist cooking, so you can get a crunchy baked dish or a juicy roast.</p><p></p><p><strong>Within the temperature range of 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Using High Density Insulation and Tangential Cooling Ventilation</strong></p><p>Protects the kitchen and its furniture from dangerously high temperatures.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grill Coil that Folds for Easy Cleaning</strong></p><p>The electric heating element of the grill can be lowered for easier cleaning of the top part of the cavity, thanks to the articulated support.</p><p></p><p><strong>Dishwasher Safe Enamel</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Features of the Oven. UOV 80 E3 TFT Silver</strong></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li>The pizza party</li><li>Warming up</li><li>Prolonged cooking</li><li>Getting started quickly</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Recipes viewed from above</li><li>Steaming food cooked in the air</li><li>From the ground up, cook</li><li>Steaming food from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Normal static cooking that is moist</li><li>Using multiple fan cooking options</li><li>Various wet fan cooking methods</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Party Pizza</strong></p><p>This oven is perfect for baking pizza, bread, focaccia, and other similar foods. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and it works in tandem with the other, less powerful heating elements to provide the ideal conditions for baking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Warming up</strong></p><p>Guarantees rapid thawing of any and all frozen foods, bringing them to room temperature without changing their flavor or texture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>This steam-discharge cooker guarantees rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for foods that require a crunchy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, fish with a salt crust, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Easy Beginning</strong></p><p>With the fast preheating function, you can quickly get to the temperature you want, and then select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also double as a rapid defroster.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling with a Fan</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enclosure for Grilling</strong></p><p>Ideal for searing fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and even veggies quickly and thoroughly, as well as browning and roasting meat in general.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc., all benefit from browning and the finishing touch of color that this function provides.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Lessons in Home Cooking</strong></p><p>With the exception of leavened desserts (biscuits, meringues, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking pastries.</p><p></p><p><strong>In-Depth Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Cooking with Moist Static</strong></p><p>Typical static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Multiple Moist Fans</strong></p><p>This increases the amount of moisture in a standard multi-fan oven.</p><p></p><p><strong>Making Sustainable Foods</strong></p><p>Slow roasting foods, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, and delicate pastries, necessitate longer cooking times when using the ECO function, which significantly reduces power consumption. However, this cooking cycle is not meant for foods that are frozen.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measure 65 in California</strong></p><p>Health Risks: Cancer and Fertility Impairment</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">www<span>Warnings.ca.gov (P65)</span></a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/wKi6ZYNcCxY.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/re1Uo4qdmcc.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/4JuPNm3uQqU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> </div></div><br/><br/><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br/><br/></div></div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs