"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/01 Stainless Steel Bain-Marie (Double Boiler) for Hot Water Bath</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>382.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g00202\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G00202_p16240-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/02 Steam Cooker Basins</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>452.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g04001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G04001_p16241-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/040/01 Griddle Dome</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>245.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g4221208\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G4221208_p16378-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G4221208 Scroll Claw Leg (Sold by Individual Leg) (Chrome)</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>242.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"White\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Copper\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 36 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 5 Elements, 3.5 cu. ft. Total Oven Capacity (Antique White / Burnished / Solid Door) - UMI09QNS3AWB\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMI09QNS3AWB\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_170253.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_170254.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_170255.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_147526-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_147527-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_147528-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_147529-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_147530-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_147531-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWB_p13577_11082.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"9390.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202223225\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>With its traditional Italian design and state-of-the-art technology, the 36-inch Majestic induction range boasts a total oven capacity of 3.5 cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><p>Order now for delivery in 90 to 120 days!</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic, a freestanding statement-piece with a style that incorporates rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions, and technologies derived from the world of professional cooking, is a beautiful and functional fusion of form and function. It effortlessly blends into any setting while still taking center stage.</p><p></p><p>Majestic range cookers are works of art in and of themselves, but they also serve as functional kitchen appliances because of the meticulous craftsmanship that goes into their curved, all-steel designs.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Detector of remaining heat</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Function that boosts</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Protecting children</li><li>A full-touch display measuring 4.3 inches</li><li>Prevention of overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Electronic temperature control with pinpoint accuracy</li><li>Features a soft-closing mechanism for doors and drawers</li><li>Fast start</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Product Technology</strong></p><p></p><p>Although aesthetics are important, having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE offers solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, combining these factors to guarantee the best satisfaction.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies related to stovetops</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Dual-Platform Induction Cooktop</strong></p><p>Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) are a modern, practical, and safe method of cooking that combines cutting-edge technology with an elegant and modern aesthetic. Induction offers many benefits, such as safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Detector of Remaining Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>Activates the active zone until the timer goes off.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>If your induction cooktop (hob) has this capability, you can treat two adjacent zones as one and use a single command to control them both.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Management</strong></p><p>By simply gliding your finger from side to side, you can adjust the operating temperature, for instance, thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>The induction cooktop (hob) cannot be turned on using the controls once this feature has been enabled and will remain so until disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Keeping Things From Overheating and Leaking Liquids</strong></p><p>A safety feature will activate and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Impressive Size and Power: The Ovens.</strong></p><p>Our 36-inch range has a capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven that will give you plenty of room, even for large dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>The oven's temperature stays consistent throughout thanks to the electronic control, unlike with traditional ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>A 4.3-inch Full-Touch Screen</strong></p><p>With TFT technology, the screen guarantees excellent legibility, showing quick and clear graphics for every function.</p><p></p><p><strong>Our TFT display is designed to be user-friendly, comprehensive, and high resolution.</strong></p><p>Control all the functions of the single oven or both ovens with a single device: temperature, timer, and automatic cooking start and end programmer\\u2014all with one touch and at a glance\\u2014on the large display.</p><p></p><p><strong>Door with a Delicate Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p>A shock absorber is integrated into the door hinges, allowing for a quieter and more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Soft-Closing Mechanism for the Warming Drawer</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Cooking Probe</strong></p><p>The tool you need to check the internal temperature of meat, among other things.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection for Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>You can achieve a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast thanks to this system, which removes the vapors from inside the cavity, allowing you to choose a drier or more moist cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Airflow for Tangential Cooling and High-Density Insulation</strong></p><p>Keeps the kitchen and its furniture from getting too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>The Ultimate Cleaning Solution: A Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>The electric heating element of the grill can be lowered for easier cleaning of the top part of the cavity, thanks to the articulated support.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rinse-Free Enamel</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Baked Goods. UOV 80 E3 TFT LCD S</strong></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing from Freeze</li><li>Intensive culinary</li><li>Getting started with little</li><li>Extremely moist cooking</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>Starting with the base</li><li>Cooking with moisture from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Damp static regular cooking</li><li>Using multiple fan cooking</li><li>Lots of wet fan cooking</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>A Pizza Party</strong></p><p>The lower heating element, in conjunction with the other, less powerful heating elements, produces the ideal temperature and baking conditions for pizza, bread, and focaccia.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing From Freeze</strong></p><p>Guarantees rapid thawing of any and all frozen foods, bringing them to room temperature without changing their flavor or texture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking to the Extremes</strong></p><p>For foods that require a crispy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc., this steam-discharge method guarantees rapid and intense cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accelerated Launch</strong></p><p>With the fast preheating function, you can quickly get to the temperature you want, and then select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. What's more, when set to a low temperature, it can also function as rapid defrosting.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Cooked with Moisture</strong></p><p>For moist cooking, such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, chicken cacciatore, etc., it ensures rapid and intense cooking with steam block.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling with a Fan</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Methods for Grilling with a Closed Door</strong></p><p>This is the perfect setting for searing fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, vegetables, and any type of meat quickly and thoroughly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Above-Ground Cooking</strong></p><p>This function is perfect for browning and finishing a wide variety of foods; burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc. all benefit from it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Perfect for browning and finishing the color of many dishes without overcooking them, it also keeps them tender.</p><p></p><p><strong>Lessons in Home Cooking</strong></p><p>Pastries (such as biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, and so on) are best cooked in this way to finish the cooking cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>In-Depth Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>To finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture, this is the best way to do it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Standard Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, roast veal, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, etc. are all great candidates for this electric oven's classic function.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular Moist Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Typical static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>This makes regular cooking with multiple fans even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>eco-friendly food preparation</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>The 65th Proposition in California</strong></p><p>Attention: Potential Cancer and Reproductive Risks</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">www<span>Warnings.ca.gov (P65)</span></a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preloa