p-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWG_p13575_170269.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWG_p13575_170270.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWG_p13575_147544-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWG_p13575_147545-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWG_p13575_147546-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWG_p13575_147547-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWG_p13575_147548-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWG_p13575_147549-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3AWG_p13575_11090.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"9390.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202223249\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>The Majestic 36-inch induction range is a perfect example of how traditional Italian design can coexist with modern technology. It has a total oven capacity of 3.5 cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><p>Order now for delivery in 90 to 120 days!</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that exudes elegance and functionality in equal measure. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies. Despite its ability to blend into any setting, Majestic commands attention.</p><p></p><p>With their ornate details and rounded forms crafted from pure steel, majestic range cookers are kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative pieces.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Detector of remaining heat</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Booster role</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Protecting children</li><li>Full touch screen display measuring 4.3 inches</li><li>Emergency measures for overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Drawer and door with a gentle closing mechanism</li><li>Fast start</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Advancements in Product Technologies</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that guarantee the best satisfaction by combining top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies related to stovetops</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Induction Range (Oven)</strong></p><p>With their modern technology and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) make cooking a breeze. Induction offers many benefits, such as safe cooking, reduced energy consumption, safety, adjustable temperature control, and quick cooking times, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measurement of Persistent Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Timer with Built-In Stop Function</strong></p><p>Activates the active zone until the timer goes off.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>With this function, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>By simply gliding your finger from side to side, you can adjust the operating temperature, for instance, thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>After you enable this feature, you can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><p><strong>The Prevention of Overheating and Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>An automatic shutoff mechanism activates in the event of a liquid spill or overheating of the cooktop (hob).</p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Oven Solutions</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Impressive Size and Power: The Ovens.</strong></p><p>Our 36-inch range has a capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven that will give you plenty of room, even for large dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>Unlike with traditional ovens, the temperature of the oven will stay consistent thanks to the electronic control.</p><p></p><p><strong>A 4.3-inch Full-Touch Screen</strong></p><p>Displaying every function with clear and immediate graphics, the display guarantees superior readability thanks to TFT technology.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen: Easy to Use, Extensive, and Super High Resolution.</strong></p><p>With a single touch of the big screen, you can control all the features of either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously. You can set the temperature, set the timer, and program the ovens to start and stop cooking automatically.</p><p></p><p><strong>Door with a System for Soft Closing</strong></p><p>A shock absorber is integrated into the door hinges, allowing for a quieter and more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Drawer Heater with Soft-Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Cooking Probe</strong></p><p>The tool you need to check the internal temperature of meat, among other things.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection (Hot Food Preparation)</strong></p><p>The vapors are drawn out of the cavity by this system, so you can control the moisture level during cooking, giving you crispy baked dishes or juicy roasts.</p><p></p><p><strong>Wide temperature range (85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit)</strong></p><p>You can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes in an ILVE oven, whether you're proofing, cooking, roasting, or using low heat.</p><p></p><p><strong>High Density Insulation and Tangential Cooling Ventilation</strong></p><p>Protects the kitchen and its furniture from dangerously high temperatures.</p><p></p><p><strong>Effortless Cleaning with the Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rinse-Free Enamel</strong></p><p>Grease is easier to remove since it does not adhere to the surface.</p><p></p><p><strong>Features of the Oven. UOV 80 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing from Freeze</li><li>Cooking to extremes</li><li>Getting started with little</li><li>Extremely moist cooking</li><li>The cooking method of the fan grill</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Preparing moist food from below</li><li>Standard, unchanging cooking</li><li>Static, moist, typical cooking</li><li>Numerous fan-assisted cooking methods</li><li>Various wet fan cooking methods</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Pizza Party</strong></p><p>Perfect for baking pizza, bread, and focaccia. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and with the assistance of the other, less powerful heating elements, it produces the ideal conditions for this kind of cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing From Freeze</strong></p><p>Guarantees rapid thawing of any and all frozen foods, bringing them to room temperature without changing their flavor or texture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>For foods that require a crispy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc., this steam-discharge method guarantees rapid and intense cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accelerated Launch</strong></p><p>Quick preheating gets the oven to the temperature you want it to be in no time at all, and then you can select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also defrost food quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Cooking with Moisture</strong></p><p>For moist cooking, such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, chicken cacciatore, etc., it ensures rapid and intense cooking with steam block.</p><p></p><p><strong>Searing on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling in a Room with No Doors Open</strong></p><p>Ideal for searing fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and even veggies quickly and thoroughly, as well as browning and roasting meat in general.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc., all benefit from browning and the finishing touch of color that this function provides.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Excellent for browning and finishing the color of a wide variety of foods without mushiness.</p><p></p><p><strong>Preparing Food from the Ground Up</strong></p><p>Pastries (such as biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, and so on) are best cooked in this way to finish the cooking cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes Made from Scratch</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, roast veal, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, etc. are all great candidates for this electric oven's classic function.</p><p></p><p><strong>Moisturizing Static Regular Cooking</strong></p><p>Standard static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Multiple Fans</strong></p><p>You can bake a variety of foods at once without worrying about their aromas blending\\u2014lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc.\\u2014and save both time and energy thanks to this feature.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>This makes regular cooking with multiple fans even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Eating Recipes</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Proposition 65 in California</strong></p><p>CAUTIONS: Potential Cancer and Reproductive Risks</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">www<span>California's P65 Warnings website</span></a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">Sorry, but the video tag isn't compatible with your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"