115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/01 Stainless Steel Bain-Marie (Double Boiler) for Hot Water Bath</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>382.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g00202\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G00202_p16240-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/02 Steam Cooker Basins</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>452.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g04001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G04001_p16241-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/040/01 Griddle Dome</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>245.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g4221208\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G4221208_p16378-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G4221208 Scroll Claw Leg (Sold by Individual Leg) (Chrome)</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>242.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Glossy Black\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Chrome\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Solid Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 36 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 5 Elements, 3.5 cu. ft. Total Oven Capacity (Glossy Black / Brass / Solid Door) - UMI09QNS3BKG\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMI09QNS3BKG\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_170327.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_170328.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_170329.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_147616-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_147617-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_147618-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_147619-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_147620-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_147621-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BKG_p13615_11122.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"9390.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202223287\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>The Majestic 36-inch induction range is a perfect example of how traditional Italian design can coexist with modern technology. It has a total oven capacity of 3.5 cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><p>Availability: 90 - 120 days for pre-order</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that effortlessly integrates into any space while commanding attention with its striking combination of form and function. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies that are both practical and aesthetically pleasing.</p><p></p><p>Majestic range cookers are works of art in and of themselves, but they also serve as functional kitchen appliances because of the meticulous craftsmanship that goes into their curved, all-steel designs.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Detector of remaining heat</li><li>Timer with built-in stop function</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Enhancement feature</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Preventing harm to children</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Protection against overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Cabinet and door soft-closing mechanism</li><li>Fast start</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Product Technology</strong></p><p></p><p>When it comes to cooking, form follows function. ILVE puts its knowledge and expertise to work for you, providing solutions that combine high-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, ensuring the highest level of satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Stove</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Dual-Platform Induction Cooktop</strong></p><p>Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) are a modern, practical, and safe method of cooking that combines cutting-edge technology with an elegant and modern aesthetic. Induction offers many benefits, such as safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Detector of Remaining Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Timer with Built-In Stop Function</strong></p><p>Activates the active zone until the timer goes off.</p><p></p><p><strong>Bridge Management</strong></p><p>If your induction cooktop (hob) has this capability, you can treat two adjacent zones as one and use a single command to control them both.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Capability</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>By simply gliding your finger from side to side, you can adjust the operating temperature, for instance, thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Protection of Children</strong></p><p>After you enable this feature, you can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><p><strong>Safeguarding Against Overheating and Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>An automatic shutoff mechanism activates in the event of a liquid spill or overheating of the cooktop (hob).</p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Ovens: Massive Capacity and Peak Efficiency.</strong></p><p>No matter if you go with a single or double combination oven, our 36-inch range offers enough room for even the largest of dishes\\u2014its capacity is up to 4 cubic feet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Electronic Temperature Control with High Precision</strong></p><p>Unlike with traditional ovens, the temperature of the oven will stay consistent thanks to the electronic control.</p><p></p><p><strong>Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></p><p>Displaying every function with clear and immediate graphics, the display guarantees superior readability thanks to TFT technology.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>With a single touch of the big screen, you can control all the features of either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously. You can set the temperature, set the timer, and program the ovens to start and stop cooking automatically.</p><p></p><p><strong>Doors with a Gentle Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p>Shock absorbers installed in the door hinges allow for quieter, more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Soft-Closing Mechanism for the Warming Drawer</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Food Preparation Assessment Tool</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Extraction for Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>You can achieve a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast thanks to this system, which removes the vapors from inside the cavity, allowing you to choose a drier or more moist cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Temperature ranging from 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>Whether you're proofing, cooking, roasting, or cooking at a low temperature, an ILVE oven can make even the most difficult recipes taste delicious.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Inspiring Cooling Air and Dense Insulation</strong></p><p>Shields kitchen and oven-related furniture from dangerously high temperatures.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grill Coil that Folds for Easy Cleaning</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Dishwasher Safe Enamel</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Baking Processes. UOV 80 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing From Freeze</li><li>Very intense cooking</li><li>Getting started with little</li><li>Extremely moist cooking</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>An Underground Kitchen</li><li>Cooking with moisture from below</li><li>Standard, unchanging cooking</li><li>Standard static cooking with moisture</li><li>Using multiple fan cooking</li><li>Lots of wet fan cooking</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Party Pizza</strong></p><p>The lower heating element, in conjunction with the other, less powerful heating elements, produces the ideal temperature and baking conditions for pizza, bread, and focaccia.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>Ensures that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>For foods that require a crispy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc., this steam-discharge method guarantees rapid and intense cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Easy Beginning</strong></p><p>With the fast preheating function, you can quickly get to the temperature you want, and then select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. What's more, when set to a low temperature, it can also function as rapid defrosting.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>For moist cooking, such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, chicken cacciatore, etc., it ensures rapid and intense cooking with steam block.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling with a Fan</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling in a Room with No Doors Open</strong></p><p>Functions such as quick and deep grilling, browning, roasting, and cooking fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and vegetables are highly recommended.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc., all benefit from browning and the finishing touch of color that this function provides.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Lessons in Home Cooking</strong></p><p>Pastries (such as biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, and so on) are best cooked in this way to finish the cooking cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes Made from Scratch</strong></p><p>To finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture, this is the best way to do it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></p><p>Pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, roast veal, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, etc. are all great candidates for this electric oven's classic function.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Cooking with Moist Static</strong></p><p>Typical static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>When cooking with multiple fans, this increases the moisture content.</p><p></p><p><strong>Natural Food Preparation</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measure 65 in California</strong></p><p>Health Risks: Cancer and Fertility Impairment</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">www<span>visit P65Warnings.ca.gov</span></a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported