", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BUC_p13595_147640-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3BUC_p13595_11134.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"9390.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202223317\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>With a total oven capacity of 3.5 cu. ft., a 4.3-inch full-touch oven control display, an easy-clean enamel oven cavity, and a combination of traditional Italian design and modern technology, the Majestic 36-inch induction range is unmatched.</p><p>Order now for delivery in 90 to 120 days!</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that effortlessly integrates into any space while commanding attention with its striking combination of form and function. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies that are both practical and aesthetically pleasing.</p><p></p><p>The sculpted, meticulously detailed forms of majestic range cookers, crafted from pure steel, make them eye-catching kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative accents.</p><p></p><p>They are masterpieces of craftsmanship, crafted for your home's kitchen. They come in a variety of colors, including RAL Classic shades upon request, and are complemented by fine metallic finishes. They are available in a wide range of sizes, from 30 to 60 inches, and provide multiple options for installation.</p><p></p><ul><li>The indicator for residual heat</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Bridge management</li><li>Function that boosts</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Ensuring the safety of children</li><li>A 4.3-inch full-touch screen</li><li>Fire safety and prevention of overheating</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Drawer and door with a gentle closing mechanism</li><li>Getting started quickly</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Advancements in Product Technologies</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, guaranteeing the best satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Range</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Dual-Platform Induction Cooktop</strong></p><p>Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) are a modern, practical, and safe method of cooking that combines cutting-edge technology with an elegant and modern aesthetic. Induction offers many benefits, such as safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Determinant of Remaining Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Automatically Stops the Timer</strong></p><p>At the end of the specified time, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>With this feature, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Capability</strong></p><p>Puts the induction cooktop's (hob's) full power into the predetermined area, allowing you to boil and cook more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Management</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Protecting Children</strong></p><p>After you enable this feature, you can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><p><strong>Keeping Things From Overheating and Leaking Liquids</strong></p><p>An automatic shutoff mechanism activates in the event of a liquid spill or overheating of the cooktop (hob).</p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Massive and Efficient Ovens.</strong></p><p>No matter if you go with a single or double combination oven, our 36-inch range offers enough room for even the largest of dishes\\u2014its capacity is up to 4 cubic feet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>The electronic control keeps the oven temperature steady, unlike regular ovens, so it doesn't change during the cooking process.</p><p></p><p><strong>Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></p><p>The display's TFT technology guarantees excellent readability by showing quick and clear graphics for each function.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>All the controls for the oven, including temperature, timer, and automatic start/end programming, are conveniently located on the large display, so all you need is a single finger to operate either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously.</p><p></p><p><strong>Doors with a Gentle Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p>With the shock absorber installed in the door hinges, closing the door is a more gradual and noiseless process.</p><p></p><p><strong>Soft-Closing Mechanism for the Warming Drawer</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Food Preparation Tester</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Discharge of Steam for Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>If you want a crispy baked dish or a juicy roast, this system will remove the vapours from inside the cavity, giving you the option to cook it dry or wet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>You can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes in an ILVE oven, whether you're proofing, cooking, roasting, or using low heat.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Inspiring Cooling Air and Dense Insulation</strong></p><p>Keeps the kitchen and its furniture from getting too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>The Ultimate Cleaning Solution: A Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>The electric heating element of the grill can be lowered for easier cleaning of the top part of the cavity, thanks to the articulated support.</p><p></p><p><strong>Clean Enamel with Ease</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Features of the Oven. UOV 80 E3 TFT Silver</strong></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing From Freeze</li><li>Cooking to extremes</li><li>A brief introduction</li><li>Extremely moist cooking</li><li>Cooking with a fan grill</li><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Steaming food from below</li><li>Constant, everyday cooking</li><li>Cooking that is moist and static</li><li>Using a number of fans to cook</li><li>Various wet fan cooking methods</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>A Pizza Party</strong></p><p>The lower heating element, in conjunction with the other, less powerful heating elements, produces the ideal temperature and baking conditions for pizza, bread, and focaccia.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing From Freeze</strong></p><p>Guarantees rapid thawing of any and all frozen foods, bringing them to room temperature without changing their flavor or texture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking to the Extremes</strong></p><p>The steam discharge ensures rapid and intense cooking, making it ideal for foods that require a crunchy texture, such as baked potatoes and vegetables, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rapid Start</strong></p><p>Quick preheating gets the oven to the temperature you want it to be in no time at all, and then you can select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also defrost food quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extremely Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>For moist cooking, such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, chicken cacciatore, etc., it ensures rapid and intense cooking with steam block.</p><p></p><p><strong>Searing on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Open-Top Grilling with a Closed Door</strong></p><p>This is the perfect setting for searing fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, vegetables, and any type of meat quickly and thoroughly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>This function is perfect for browning and finishing a wide variety of foods; burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc. all benefit from it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Making Food from the Ground Up</strong></p><p>With the exception of leavened desserts (biscuits, meringues, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking pastries.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes Made from Scratch</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></p><p>This is the standard setting for electric ovens and is great for browning pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, roast veal, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and many more foods.</p><p></p><p><strong>Wet Static Regular Cooking</strong></p><p>This makes traditional static cooking even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>You can bake a variety of foods at once without worrying about their aromas blending\\u2014lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc.\\u2014and save both time and energy thanks to this feature.</p><p></p><p><strong>Fan Cooking with Multiple Moist Fans</strong></p><p>This increases the amount of moisture in a standard multi-fan oven.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Eating Recipes</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measure 65 in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Danger to Health and Fertility</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">www<span>California's P65 Warnings website</span></a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video co