\"/cdn/shop/files/G4221208_p16378-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G4221208 Scroll Claw Leg (Sold by Individual Leg) (Chrome)</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>242.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"White\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Chrome\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Solid Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 36 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 5 Elements, 3.5 cu. ft. Total Oven Capacity (White / Brass / Solid Door) - UMI09QNS3WHG\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMI09QNS3WHG\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_170445.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_170446.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_170447.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_147865-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_147866-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_147867-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_147868-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_147869-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_147870-1.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI09QNS3WHG_p13639_11210.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"9390.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202223515\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>With its traditional Italian design and state-of-the-art technology, the 36-inch Majestic induction range boasts a total oven capacity of 3.5 cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><p>Product Status: Available</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that effortlessly integrates into any space while commanding attention with its striking combination of form and function. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies that are both practical and aesthetically pleasing.</p><p></p><p>The graceful curves and meticulously crafted details of majestic range cookers make them beautiful additions to any home.</p><p></p><p>Designed for your home's kitchen, these workhorses are available in a variety of colors (from 30 to 60 inches) and set-up options (from multiple options) and can be customized to RAL Classic shades upon request. They also feature fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Measurement of remaining heat</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Manage bridges</li><li>Function that boosts</li><li>Handles for sliding</li><li>Ensuring children's safety</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Protecting against overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Cabinet and door soft-closing mechanism</li><li>Getting started with little</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Product Technology</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, guaranteeing the best satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies related to stovetops</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Induction Range (Oven)</strong></p><p>With their modern technology and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) make cooking a breeze. Induction offers many benefits, such as safe cooking, reduced energy consumption, safety, adjustable temperature control, and quick cooking times, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measurement of Persistent Heat</strong></p><p>The glass is hot, so be careful not to touch it or put anything on it; doing so could cause damage.</p><p></p><p><strong>Automatically Stops the Timer</strong></p><p>Once the specified time has passed, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Managing Bridges</strong></p><p>With this function, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Capability</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>By simply gliding your finger from side to side, you can adjust the operating temperature, for instance, thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Protection of Children</strong></p><p>After you enable this feature, you can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><p><strong>Preventing Liquid Spills and Overheating</strong></p><p>An automatic shutoff mechanism activates in the event of a liquid spill or overheating of the cooktop (hob).</p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Massive and Efficient Ovens.</strong></p><p>Our 36-inch range has a capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven that will give you plenty of room, even for large dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Controlling Temperature with Electronic Precision</strong></p><p>Unlike with traditional ovens, the temperature of the oven will stay consistent thanks to the electronic control.</p><p></p><p><strong>A 4.3-inch Full-Touch Screen</strong></p><p>Displaying every function with clear and immediate graphics, the display guarantees superior readability thanks to TFT technology.</p><p></p><p><strong>Our TFT display is designed to be user-friendly, comprehensive, and high resolution.</strong></p><p>With a single touch of the big screen, you can control all the features of either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously. You can set the temperature, set the timer, and program the ovens to start and stop cooking automatically.</p><p></p><p><strong>Door with a Delicate Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p>Shock absorbers installed in the door hinges allow for quieter, more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Soft-Closing Mechanism for the Warming Drawer</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Food Preparation Tester</strong></p><p>The tool you need to check the internal temperature of meat, among other things.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection for Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>You can achieve a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast thanks to this system, which removes the vapors from inside the cavity, allowing you to choose a drier or more moist cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>Whether you're proofing, cooking, roasting, or cooking at a low temperature, an ILVE oven can make even the most difficult recipes taste delicious.</p><p></p><p><strong>Effective Ventilation for Tangential Cooling and High Density Insulation</strong></p><p>Keeps the kitchen and its furniture from getting too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Effortless Cleaning with the Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Dishwasher Safe Enamel</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Baking Processes. UOV 80 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing from Freeze</li><li>Thorough cooking</li><li>Fast start</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Steaming food cooked in the air</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Using moisture from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Normal static cooking that is moist</li><li>Using a number of fans to cook</li><li>Several wet fan ovens</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>A Pizza Party</strong></p><p>Perfect for baking pizza, bread, and focaccia. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and with the assistance of the other, less powerful heating elements, it produces the ideal conditions for this kind of cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing From Freeze</strong></p><p>Guarantees rapid thawing of any and all frozen foods, bringing them to room temperature without changing their flavor or texture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking to the Extremes</strong></p><p>This steam-discharge cooker guarantees rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for foods that require a crunchy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, fish with a salt crust, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rapid Start</strong></p><p>Quick preheating gets the oven to the temperature you want it to be in no time at all, and then you can select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also defrost food quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extremely Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>For moist cooking, such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, chicken cacciatore, etc., it ensures rapid and intense cooking with steam block.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling under Covered Spaces</strong></p><p>Ideal for searing fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and even veggies quickly and thoroughly, as well as browning and roasting meat in general.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc., all benefit from browning and the finishing touch of color that this function provides.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Lessons in Home Cooking</strong></p><p>When it comes to pastries (biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish the cooking cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>In-Depth Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, roast veal, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, etc. are all great candidates for this electric oven's classic function.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy, Regular, Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>This makes traditional static cooking even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Multiple Fans</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>When cooking with multiple fans, this increases the moisture content.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Eating Recipes</strong></p><p>Slow roasting foods, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, and delicate pastries, necessitate longer cooking times when using the ECO function, which significantly reduces power consumption. However, this cooking cycle is not meant for foods that are frozen.</p><p></p><p><strong>The 65th Proposition in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Possible Cancer and Harm to Fertility</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">www<span>Warnings.ca.gov (P65)</span></a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/wKi6ZYNcCxY.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/re1Uo4qdmcc.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/4JuPNm3uQqU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem